{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-antv-gatsby-theme-antv-0-10-5-antv-gatsby-theme-antv-site-templates-document-tsx","path":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/visual","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"AntV","githubUrl":"https://github.com/antvis","docs":[{"slug":"specification/principles","title":{"zh":"设计原则","en":"Design Principles"},"order":0},{"slug":"specification/components","title":{"zh":"图表组件设计指引","en":"Design for Components of Charts"},"order":1}]},"pathPrefix":""},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>AntV 色板（ 数据可视化色彩体系）是基于  <a href=\"https://ant.design/docs/spec/colors-cn\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ant Design 色彩体系</a>，并结合数据可视化特性而设计的。<br />在数据可视化设计中，色彩的运用原则上应首先考虑准确性，先保证达到了信息传递、操作指引、交互反馈，或是强化、凸显某一个信息的目的，其次再去考虑品牌识别性。</p>\n<p>选择 AntV 色彩时有以下三个注意点：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>根据不同的数据特性选择相应的色彩，保证数据传达的准确性；</li>\n<li>结合当前页面环境，建立视觉连续性；</li>\n<li>视觉层次清晰可辨，保证色彩足够的对比度的同时也能够被视障碍（色盲、色弱）的用户辨别。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p>在可视化领域中，数据信息到颜色的映射是非常重要的一个环节，分为色调、饱和度、亮度三个视觉通道。通常色调属于分类的视觉通道，饱和度和亮度通常用于连续的视觉通道。</p>\n<p>AntV 色板包含分类色板、连续色板和语义色板，用户选择色板时需对照数据特性选择相应的配色方案。</p>\n<h2 id=\"分类色板\"><a href=\"#%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E8%89%B2%E6%9D%BF\" aria-label=\"分类色板 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>分类色板</h2>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*XUT3T7L71bwAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=478/>\n<h2 id=\"连续色板\"><a href=\"#%E8%BF%9E%E7%BB%AD%E8%89%B2%E6%9D%BF\" aria-label=\"连续色板 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>连续色板</h2>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*DBFTS4jnrAoAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Ant Design 的色彩生成算法工具提供了<a href=\"https://ant.design/docs/spec/colors-cn#%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%89%B2%E6%9D%BF\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"nofollow\"> 12 种连续色板</a>。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"语义色板\"><a href=\"#%E8%AF%AD%E4%B9%89%E8%89%B2%E6%9D%BF\" aria-label=\"语义色板 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>语义色板</h2>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*rnGzSoja17YAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"使用指南\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97\" aria-label=\"使用指南 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使用指南</h2>\n<p>我们发现，在提供官方色板的前提下，仍有用户并不是十分擅长在实际场景中应用色板。在此我们提出几个设计指引供参考</p>\n<h3 id=\"生成自己的色板\"><a href=\"#%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E6%9D%BF\" aria-label=\"生成自己的色板 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>生成自己的色板</h3>\n<p>如果你想生成一套自己的色板，那么我们建议您需要遵循以下原则，查看更多色板分析：<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/70121039\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/70121039</a></p>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*bNf5TqyehdEAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>\n<h3 id=\"避免使用过多的颜色数量\"><a href=\"#%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%9A%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2%E6%95%B0%E9%87%8F\" aria-label=\"避免使用过多的颜色数量 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>避免使用过多的颜色数量</h3>\n<p>在实际应用中，经常会出现大量颜色使用的误区，建议高亮重要的数据（不超过 8 个），其他数据默认置灰，通过图例交互进行查看。</p>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*r01PSYbo5lwAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=600/>\n<h3 id=\"数据映射的规则尽量简单\"><a href=\"#%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E6%98%A0%E5%B0%84%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%99%E5%B0%BD%E9%87%8F%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95\" aria-label=\"数据映射的规则尽量简单 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>数据映射的规则尽量简单</h3>\n<p>同样的数据，映射规则尽量保持为一种。<br />例如当使用柱形的高度来映射数据时，就不需要再加上颜色的维度去映射数据了。</p>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*DdcHQYrSO_IAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=600/>\n<h3 id=\"对应数据，做到准确的映射\"><a href=\"#%E5%AF%B9%E5%BA%94%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%81%9A%E5%88%B0%E5%87%86%E7%A1%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%98%A0%E5%B0%84\" aria-label=\"对应数据，做到准确的映射 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>对应数据，做到准确的映射</h3>\n<p>对应自己的数据，按照数据特性选用对的色板，下图中分类数据应选用分类色板，而不是连续色板。</p>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*UPgcSLEmTnkAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=600/>\n<h3 id=\"解释你的颜色\"><a href=\"#%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8A%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2\" aria-label=\"解释你的颜色 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>解释你的颜色</h3>\n<p>当图表中出现不同颜色时，需要向读者解释颜色代表的含义。</p>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*TMw5RYDOcAsAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=600/>\n<h3 id=\"上下文保持颜色的一致性\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8B%E6%96%87%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E6%80%A7\" aria-label=\"上下文保持颜色的一致性 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>上下文保持颜色的一致性</h3>\n<p>对于统一度量，使用同样的颜色方案，而且在整个页面（通常是仪表盘）使用时，注意保持整体颜色方案的一致性。</p>\n<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*LcXRRL30oDwAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/principles/visual/#%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E8%89%B2%E6%9D%BF\">分类色板</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/principles/visual/#%E8%BF%9E%E7%BB%AD%E8%89%B2%E6%9D%BF\">连续色板</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/principles/visual/#%E8%AF%AD%E4%B9%89%E8%89%B2%E6%9D%BF\">语义色板</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/principles/visual/#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97\">使用指南</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/principles/visual/#%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E8%89%B2%E6%9D%BF\">生成自己的色板</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/principles/visual/#%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%BF%87%E5%A4%9A%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2%E6%95%B0%E9%87%8F\">避免使用过多的颜色数量</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/principles/visual/#%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E6%98%A0%E5%B0%84%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%84%E5%88%99%E5%B0%BD%E9%87%8F%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95\">数据映射的规则尽量简单</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/principles/visual/#%E5%AF%B9%E5%BA%94%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%EF%BC%8C%E5%81%9A%E5%88%B0%E5%87%86%E7%A1%AE%E7%9A%84%E6%98%A0%E5%B0%84\">对应数据，做到准确的映射</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/principles/visual/#%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8A%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2\">解释你的颜色</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/zh/docs/specification/principles/visual/#%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8B%E6%96%87%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E8%87%B4%E6%80%A7\">上下文保持颜色的一致性</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/visual","readingTime":{"text":"1 min read","time":25200}},"frontmatter":{"title":"视觉"},"parent":{"__typename":"File","relativePath":"specification/principles/visual.zh.md"}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/basic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"设计原则","order":0}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles/basic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Principles","order":0}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles/visual"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Visual","order":1}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/visual"},"frontmatter":{"title":"视觉","order":1}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/interact"},"frontmatter":{"title":"交互","order":2}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles/interact"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Interact","order":2}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/titlenotes"},"frontmatter":{"title":"标题与注释","order":3}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/titlenotes"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Title and Notes","order":3}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/mobile"},"frontmatter":{"title":"移动","order":3}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/principles/mobile"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Mobile","order":3}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/axis"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Axis","order":4}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/axis"},"frontmatter":{"title":"轴","order":4}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/legend"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Legend","order":5}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/legend"},"frontmatter":{"title":"图例","order":5}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/label"},"frontmatter":{"title":"标签","order":6}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/label"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Label","order":6}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/graphic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tooltip","order":7}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/components/tooltip"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tooltip","order":7}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/tooltip"},"frontmatter":{"title":"提示信息","order":7}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/graphic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"图形设计指引","order":8}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/resources"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Resource Download","order":10}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/resources"},"frontmatter":{"title":"资源下载","order":10}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/reference"},"frontmatter":{"title":"经典文献","order":11}}},{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/en/docs/specification/reference"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Classical Literature","order":11}}}]}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"prev":{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/principles/basic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"设计原则","order":0},"html":"<p>AntV 数据可视化设计原则是基于  <a href=\"https://ant.design/docs/spec/introduce-cn\" target=\"_self\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ant Design</a>  设计体系衍生的，具有数据可视化特性的指导原则。它遵循 Ant Design 设计价值观的同时，对数据可视化领域的进一步解读，如色彩、字体的指引。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>注：Ant Design 是一个致力于提升『用户』和『设计者』使用体验的中台设计语言。它将进行 UE 设计和 UI 设计人员统称为『设计者』，利用统一的规范进行设计赋能，全面提高中台产品体验和研发效率。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>我们经过大量的项目实践和经验总结，总结了以下四条核心原则，并以重要等级进行排序，四条原则相辅相成且呈递进关系，希望你在设计时也可以采纳。</p>\n<p><a name=\"910cly\"></a></p>\n<h3 id=\"准确\"><a href=\"#%E5%87%86%E7%A1%AE\" aria-label=\"准确 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>准确</strong></h3>\n<p>从数据转化到可视表达时不歪曲，不误导，不遗漏，忠实反映数据里包含的信息。</p>\n<p><a name=\"e45eqz\"></a></p>\n<h3 id=\"有效\"><a href=\"#%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88\" aria-label=\"有效 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>有效</strong></h3>\n<p>信息传达有重点，克制不冗余，避免信息过载，用最适量的数据-油墨比（Data-ink Ratio）表达对用户最有用的信息。</p>\n<p><a name=\"u9e7nl\"></a></p>\n<h3 id=\"清晰\"><a href=\"#%E6%B8%85%E6%99%B0\" aria-label=\"清晰 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>清晰</strong></h3>\n<p>表现方式清楚易读，具条理性，可以帮助用户快速达成目标，在最少的时间内获取更多的信息。</p>\n<p><a name=\"po8hot\"></a></p>\n<h3 id=\"美\"><a href=\"#%E7%BE%8E\" aria-label=\"美 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>美</strong></h3>\n<p>对数据的完美表达，合理利用视觉元素进行艺术创作，不过度修饰，给用户优雅的体验。</p>\n<hr>\n<ol>\n<li>注 1 : Data-ink Ratio, Edward Tufte, The Visual Display of Quantitative Information, p. 51.</li>\n</ol>"}},"next":{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/zh/docs/specification/components/graphic"},"frontmatter":{"title":"图形设计指引","order":8},"html":"<h2 id=\"定义\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\" aria-label=\"定义 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>定义</h2>\n<p>图形是统计图表的视觉通道在形状上映射的视觉展现，是图表的主体部分，其他图表组件的目的是帮助读者更好地理解数据在图形上的映射关系。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"何时使用\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%95%E6%97%B6%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\" aria-label=\"何时使用 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>何时使用</h2>\n<p>图形可以通过视觉特征更快地被读者感知和接受。从认知学的角度，人眼在对图形的获取效率远高于对抽象意符的理解。所以图形是数据可视化的必备元素，承载着数据背后蕴含的信息。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"类型\"><a href=\"#%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B\" aria-label=\"类型 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>类型</h2>\n<p>按照基础图表类型，图形可分为：折线，面积，散点，气泡，饼/环，柱形，条形。<br /><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/mdn/rms_f8c6a0/afts/img/A*RdOVQ5Sv3UIAAAAAAAAAAABkARQnAQ' width=750/></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"样式\"><a href=\"#%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F\" aria-label=\"样式 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>样式</h2>\n<p>二维空间内的统计图表图形属性遵循计算机视觉元素构成，有 填充，描边，阴影等样式。</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"用法建议\"><a href=\"#%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE\" aria-label=\"用法建议 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>用法建议</h2>\n<h4 id=\"图形比例\"><a href=\"#%E5%9B%BE%E5%BD%A2%E6%AF%94%E4%BE%8B\" aria-label=\"图形比例 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>图形比例</h4>\n<p>以柱形图为例，柱子比例和两边间距的比例为 1：2：1，柱子宽度为总宽度的 60%。</p>\n<h4 id=\"填充样式\"><a href=\"#%E5%A1%AB%E5%85%85%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F\" aria-label=\"填充样式 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>填充样式</h4>\n<p>根据图形元素在实际图表中的面积占比，我们定义了相应的填充样式。图形占比越大的图表，对应填充的透明度越高。如，在柱/条形图中，图形的填充比例为 95%；在面积图中，图形的填充比例为 25%。<img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/basement_prod/8fda1e44-7562-445a-9539-87044e1d02ba.svg' width=339/><img src='https://gw.alipayobjects.com/zos/basement_prod/a86e85af-1893-4fe3-bc5c-74784ef7801a.svg' width=341/></p>\n<p>持续更新中，敬请期待…</p>"}}}}}